HEADWORD: Nitrol
<hw>Ni"trol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Any
one of a series of hydrocarbons containing the nitro and the nitroso or
isonitroso group united to the same carbon atom.</def>⟦br⟧
